summary: I felt like drawing more of my little Chiichu, he's just too damn cute! - Like most citizens of the valley, Chiichu has a...
caption:
I felt like drawing more of my little Chiichu, he’s just too damn cute!

- Like most citizens of the valley, Chiichu has a strange relationship with Snufkin. He often just follows the lonely travelers footprints and mimic his tunes in progress. Though since Snuf isn’t a big fan of children, he’s try to shoo off the young Chiicbubii to no avail

- He also likes being around Little My (Mostly cause they’re around the same age). Though she’ll poke fun at him and tease him about his little habits, he still loves being around her~

- Chiichu’s been around the valley for the last few years (in their world of course) yet he’s still a mystery. Nobody knows where he came from, what he is or even where he lives. Whenever you ask, he just draws a picture of a random house; mostly the Moomin Household. I don’t even think he knows the answer to that question

On ships over seas
that I now know

blog.description: Hello! Please call me Jir! While I reblog lots of things my art is all under my Moominvalley tag, please check it out! I'm a 21 year old girl with High functioning Autism from Canada. My current biggest fandom is Moomins with my favourite character being Snufkin. I am also a fan of Wander over Yonder, Star vs the Forces of Evil, Steven Universe, Ducktales, Undertale, Gravity Falls, the Adventure Zone, OK KO and We Bare Bears. If you have any questions or just want to tell me something, go right ahead, don't be afraid to ask! Just please nothing rude.
